com.epoch
Class Response

java.lang.Object
  com.epoch.Response
All Implemented Interfaces:
QuestionConstants, ResponseConstants, XMLConstants
public class Response
extends Object
implements QuestionConstants, ResponseConstants

Stores the student's response and parsed & processed versions of it. The purpose is to avoid repeated execution of the same processing steps for different evaluators.

                         String variablePart,

Translates feedback, perhaps substituting a variable part of a phrase into the feedback.

Parameters:
qType - mechanism or synthesis
englFeedback - feedback to be translated
variablePart - phrase to be substituted into the translated feedback
condition - whether we might expect to substitute a variable part: if there's a verification error, or if it's a synthesis response that uses reagents that should come off the reagent menu
Returns:
translated feedback
